 從來唔單係一個因 而係好多因素聚集而成 <br />\n而拍拖後相處成點先係最重要<br />\n如果你地唔夾 好無火花 好無默契 到最後一樣會唔再愛對方/分手<br />\n情感係一時 感情係長久"},{"pid":"2e87d49e6e97146aabc1625ea85dba432b219302","tid":1956541,"uid":50762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5320e088547d9b332ddc72d14ea581992e7b24cd","tid":1956541,"uid":25659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f584330c8f38bd829f42be7bcb1f039a148620e","tid":1956541,"uid":351518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T18:27:48.000Z","msg":"有時見到啲朋友放閃就好想自己都有拖拍 但諗深一層就算真係比你到搵 但相處時又無咩話題 大家都好辛苦到時又唔開心 倒不如自己一個仲好 慢慢等到真係相處舒服既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實我都想比人愛架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T18:51:00.000Z","msg":"絲打我同你一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰陣見有朋友拍拖結婚自己仲係一個人真係好想搵個人拍<br />\n於是去識人又主動約異性朋友<br />\n後來冷靜左 發覺自己一個真係好舒服<br />\n連覆對方msg都覺得攰<br />\nFeel到對方未feel到我冷淡咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌我真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T19:00:21.000Z","msg":"除左因為冷靜左覺得一個人真係好舒服<br />\n有無諗過都反映你地唔夾 你同佢相處得唔舒服 你地之間唔夠默契同火花<br />\n有時同一個人相處得舒服都係感覺黎 你未必明確知原因 但有時就係咁人夾人<br />\n如果咁樣諗 你覺得你真係仆街咩？<br />\n你只係發現你地唔夾咋喎 <br />\n拍拖唔夾都會分手啦 更何況未一齊了解中？"},{"pid":"e0407b71e706669ab3c9255b4d239fdfaca2c4a0","tid":1956541,"uid":265403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"167f34dc055a91cce188ee7fc1f37faf264a1e58","tid":1956541,"uid":287457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e13014c3c9c76eed5bf5473d4e8d096b3def247d","tid":1956541,"uid":265403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a8b7a72d39a6c9b64d2061f312b34856d7a1c3d","tid":1956541,"uid":253295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T10:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T10:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T01:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37dbe8a81a7f419b389970b94071210efe27686","tid":1956541,"uid":253295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d3fab803959dc092dfaaac642fc5f73e853b650","tid":1956541,"uid":50762,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T18:55:41.000Z","msg":"標題有啲問題<br />\n你應該係想問 太寂寞想拍拖定真係鍾意果個人<br />\n<br />\n其實好簡單就係拓展你生活圈子<br />\n當出現多於一位異性 而你係有興趣多啲 <br />\n咁至少代表你好感<br />\n可能你話咁都只係因為想拍拖而二揀一發展姐<br />\n但其實某程度上我覺得因咩而開始拍拖唔重要 應該話唔需要分得咁清楚 甚至係無得分得咁清楚<br />\n因為要結一個果 從來唔單係一個因 而係好多因素聚集而成 <br />\n而拍拖後相處成點先係最重要<br />\n如果你地唔夾 好無火花 好無默契 到最後一樣會唔再愛對方/分手<br />\n情感係一時 感情係長久"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T04:44:07.000Z","msg":"其實我意思係<br />\n如果因為寂寞先同人一齊好似只係想取暖<br />\n可能冇認真了解好一個人甚至係比感覺蒙蔽左以為自己好中意對方<br />\n因為拍到某個階段就好迷失覺得所有野太快<br />\n再衰d感覺似負左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5357a3c1859627d843462b1d25f46fd5d32233c4","tid":1956541,"uid":241879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c0c71b581bbd0a88741eb04c3ab668d7afca03c","tid":1956541,"uid":253295,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"db6288d45ee2259a22968770da1cfe7d0918a4f5","tid":1956541,"uid":149849,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:58:09.000Z","msg":"其實你係怕比人hurt姐 唔係唔想拍拖"},{"pid":"ee9dcc59e3fffa7bd769a356e6dccdaee7d56e7f","tid":1956541,"uid":253295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b91457cdb5acc7ac6787d46ca046637c8250335","tid":1956541,"uid":246422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8dea879c132f4a9c0f3edfd38b2c9633ba822082","tid":1956541,"uid":253295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2d1da66e871ac59a813adf3fc9677b908b139d0","tid":1956541,"uid":246422,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:48:22.000Z","msg":"有時係好想有個人陪自己出去行街食飯睇戲 想有個人掛住吓 <br />\n但又發覺係未放低前一個 都係自閉吓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有疫情影響"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T10:21:48.000Z","msg":"唯有同自己講感覺係暫時，一陣就會走"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T10:23:17.000Z","msg":"但自己一個真係好悶 唔想成日痴住fd<br />\n所以我係太寂寞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T07:10:52.000Z","msg":"我都係 但我明唔應該太依賴人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太依賴又無端端痴線以為自己中意左人"}]}